{"tid":828810,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚鼻鼾撚","createTime":"2018-09-20T03:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T11:02:06.000Z","uid":12468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15301ad3b64a1328b177d596247cbcae45c93952","tid":828810,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:07:51.000Z","msg":"自己瞓覺有鼻鼾聲比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n追左幾個post大概上有呢幾個方法<br />\n<br />\n1) 做脷操<br />\n呢個好似有少少用但要keep住做好煩 同成效唔穩定 好睇你狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 痴鼻貼<br />\n都幾貴 $50得15塊 如果有其他好d嘅方法會更好 定還是攞普通膠紙痴都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 打側瞓<br />\n我未習慣 咁多年黎都要平瞓先瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4) 買d防鼻鼾產品<br />\n有d好on9 如果你有鼻鼾聲就電一電你等你瞓得無咁好就無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到有個眼罩叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴住就可以無聲 想試下佢<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲試過舊野或者有無其他方法有用一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b63394f9ca0f125a515e7ccc8dd71bbe962871","tid":828810,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"減肥啦"},{"pid":"1595ed792493261969a31193ccba251e139aa6c6","tid":828810,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75b63394f9ca0f125a515e7ccc8dd71bbe962871","tid":828810,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"減肥啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"好撚瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  174左右 60kg"},{"pid":"d8120f4d4047605d47a92afe6a43621698f08a4a","tid":828810,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"係咪未瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffc766dd9130d210c03ce5a4fe9ead9502a1a1f","tid":828810,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e244f1bc40b49f635e6febfb55abba04af7ab2","tid":828810,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"我唔信連登無鼻鼾撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b2366407c9499c4589c8c20773bab9a68c24c5","tid":828810,"uid":155558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:38:32.000Z","msg":"用緊睡眠呼吸機，完全無晒鼻鼾聲，睡眠質素仲好咗，起身之後個人好精神。仲有就係睡眠呼吸機有filter，吸入嘅空氣都經過過濾，鼻敏感都由嚴重轉做無乜鼻敏感。<br />\n<br />\n唔好處：要帶頭罩再拖住條氣喉，但習慣咗就無乜嘢，最緊要個人健康係無價，所以依家每晚都要用，去旅行都帶埋去。"},{"pid":"ab0604cb407734d57cd8b48a3825ddb8b6b7ddab","tid":828810,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b2366407c9499c4589c8c20773bab9a68c24c5","tid":828810,"uid":155558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:38:32.000Z","msg":"用緊睡眠呼吸機，完全無晒鼻鼾聲，睡眠質素仲好咗，起身之後個人好精神。仲有就係睡眠呼吸機有filter，吸入嘅空氣都經過過濾，鼻敏感都由嚴重轉做無乜鼻敏感。<br />\n<br />\n唔好處：要帶頭罩再拖住條氣喉，但習慣咗就無乜嘢，最緊要個人健康係無價，所以依家每晚都要用，去旅行都帶埋去。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"係咁意google左d圖 部機成部ps4 size<br />\n但我瞓上格床無位擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2be07971362a4ec689db3a3d1a5c4580fe6426","tid":828810,"uid":155558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab0604cb407734d57cd8b48a3825ddb8b6b7ddab","tid":828810,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b2366407c9499c4589c8c20773bab9a68c24c5","tid":828810,"uid":155